{"tid":1461161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.18 (終於成材) 民陣擬周日由維園遊行至遮打道　要求政府回應五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75f1a2ac5289e4bbfefd44cf7461d9bb412d28a7","tid":1461161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"民陣計劃本月18日發起遊行，下午3時由銅鑼灣維園起步，終點是中環遮打道，要求政府回應市民五大訴求，以及聲討警方濫用武力，民陣申請遊行人數有30萬。<br />\n<br />\n召集人岑子杰表示，警方違法鎮壓示威者的情況愈來愈嚴重，包括日前在港鐵站施放催淚彈，製造「毒氣室」、用布袋彈直射示威者眼睛等，無視武力指引及人權標準。<br />\n<br />\n他又質疑，721元朗白衣人無差別襲擊當日，有懷疑是黑社會分子手持鐵通等武器，但警方表示看不到，到今日被捕人士只是被暫控非法集結，反問不是「警黑勾結」是甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰說，今日出現的示威是因為特首林鄭月娥拒聽民意，製造政治動盪但不願「收科」，將全部罪名怪責示威者，質疑問責官員不問責、紀律部隊無紀律，將示威者抹黑成暴徒，等同警方可無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n他批評林鄭月娥指示威影響經濟及民生，等同開出命題，究竟港人要「麵包」或「自由」，相信市民有良知，會繼續出來遊行。<br />\n<br />\n至於原訂星期日舉行的「荃葵青遊行」，相關主辦者表示，為響應民陣的遊行，會延至本月25日。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474371-20190813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474371-20190813.htm&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=d4381f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474371-20190813.htm&h=4371edf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474371-20190813.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eabc9a272c3f63365569afe180ed825c0f606832","tid":1461161,"uid":267328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣？即share"},{"pid":"5bfeb60d9ff5d21316df76e4c21c7240d1e9bcb3","tid":1461161,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46ae30300a2027c104189c216df6cf7644650fc1","tid":1461161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/286/5d523d9e4d549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F286%2F5d523d9e4d549.jpg&h=c8915093&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa25d851f8d5ee5877f39f8ef5534f098d7f321","tid":1461161,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00w8qkb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00w8qkb.jpg&h=6e198978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2409193312461379/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2409193312461379%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=b8fc6b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2409193312461379/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"26b8132d5b426a77475692537a7482eef9afeb27","tid":1461161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d284f259f31654b6d87cc4affb4d20da54f6b42e","tid":1461161,"uid":82183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"又維園集合根本無用。依家係要喺赤鱲角遊行，同時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">令到民航處總部無得正常運作，達到影響航運嘅第2重打擊，D既得利益者先會回應你</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n機場為香港命脈，機場、3貨運大樓、民航處總部，集思廣益<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458921/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458921/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下個POST啦，一定有用過你去維園</span></strong>"},{"pid":"894fd18d49ee01c510edc653e83e4501486075b9","tid":1461161,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"今次4，5點先過來<br />\n<br />\n咁撚熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650e4ae486487a171ce9a1a808af9dbb6c19d965","tid":1461161,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"今次要谷夠300期人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0672265b8a344ac4ce53dc54eb23c780849aa9","tid":1461161,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"650e4ae486487a171ce9a1a808af9dbb6c19d965","tid":1461161,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"今次要谷夠300期人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"*萬"}]}